    public class TriggerDef
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.thrift.TBase<TriggerDef,TriggerDef._Fields>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<TriggerDef>
    Describes a trigger. `options` should include at least 'class' param. Other options are not supported yet.
